[
    "define",
    true,
    [
        "try",
        "body",
        "handlers"
    ],
    "[\"try\", <body>, <handlers>]\n\nCatches and handles errors. The `handlers` is an object mapping error type to handler; it will be expanded using [[obj]].\nDuring evaluation of the body, if an error is thrown, the error's `type` (as returned by [[with]]) will be checked to see if it's in the handlers, and if it is, the handler is called with the `message` and `context` of the error.\nIf no handler directly matches, the special catch-all handler `\"\\*\"` is tried, and if it exists, it is called with `type`, `message` and `context`.\nIn both cases if the handler exists, `true` is returned to [[with]] to stop propagation of the error. If the handler wants to propagate the error, it should re-throw it using [[error]].\nIf `body` exits cleanly with no error, the special `\"else\"` handler is called with no arguments, if present.",
    [
        "~",
        [
            "let",
            [
                [
                    "handlers",
                    [
                        "obj",
                        [
                            ",",
                            [
                                "$",
                                "handlers"
                            ]
                        ]
                    ]
                ]
            ],
            [
                "with",
                null,
                [
                    "obj",
                    {
                        "exit": [
                            "lambda",
                            [
                                "k",
                                "type",
                                "value",
                                "ctx"
                            ],
                            [
                                "let",
                                [
                                    [
                                        "handler",
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            [
                                                "handlers",
                                                [
                                                    "$",
                                                    "type"
                                                ]
                                            ]
                                        ]
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "starHandler",
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            [
                                                "handlers",
                                                "*"
                                            ]
                                        ]
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "elseHandler",
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            [
                                                "handlers",
                                                "else"
                                            ]
                                        ]
                                    ]
                                ],
                                [
                                    "unless",
                                    [
                                        "$",
                                        "type"
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "when",
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            "elseHandler"
                                        ],
                                        [
                                            "elseHandler"
                                        ]
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "return",
                                        true
                                    ]
                                ],
                                [
                                    "when",
                                    [
                                        "$",
                                        "handler"
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "handler",
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            "value"
                                        ],
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            "ctx"
                                        ]
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "return",
                                        true
                                    ]
                                ],
                                [
                                    "when",
                                    [
                                        "$",
                                        "starHandler"
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "starHandler",
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            "type"
                                        ],
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            "value"
                                        ],
                                        [
                                            "$",
                                            "ctx"
                                        ]
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "return",
                                        true
                                    ]
                                ],
                                false
                            ]
                        ]
                    }
                ],
                [
                    ",",
                    [
                        "$",
                        "body"
                    ]
                ]
            ]
        ]
    ]
]